snippet.textDisplay: Grammys don’t define artists. But still, she still deserved one. This performance looked like a lot of thought and time was put in it and didn’t win a Grammy. She released thank u, next 6 MONTHS ACTER SWEETENER AND IT IS AMAZING. she got nominated for not 1 not 2 but 5 GRAMMYS, and went home empty handed. She went on tour for so damn long, and it was last minute and it was so amazing yet she didn’t get a Grammy. I love Billie but still, she would have been fine with AT LEAST 1 Grammy but no. Either way she still slayed both the red carpet AND her performance. I still think Billie is awesome for winning that much Grammys at the age of 18, but Ariana has been here for so damn long and deserved a Grammy. I still am looking forward to Ariana’s next track or album but if we do get a new song or album, it won’t be anytime soon since she worked so hard on the SWT and is taking a break for her mental and physical health. Speaking of the tour, the tour was breathtaking. I’m still really disappointed in the fact that she did not win a Grammy. ariana definitely got snubbed
